column4: Microsoft made $1.3 billion in cash payments in GitHub deal
column5: Microsoft Corp  said in a filing late Thursday it had made $1.3 billion in cash payments in connection to its acquisition of coding hosting startup GitHub.

column4: ChargePoint gives Europe equal billing in electric car grid plan
column5: LISBON  Nov 9 ChargePoint  which operates one of the world's largest charging station grids for electric vehicles  expects to split a major    expansion plan equally between Europe and its home market the United States  its chief executive said.
